quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  41,21,aur woh apne chumron ( yani aaza ) se kahin ge ke tum ne hamaray khilaaf kyun shahadat di? woh kahin ge ke jis khuda ne sab cheezon ko nutq bakhsha isi ne hum ko bhi goyai di aur isi ne tum ko pehli baar pedakiya tha aur isi ki taraf tum ko lout kar jana hai
  41,22,aur tum is ( baat ke khauf ) se to parda nahi karte they ke tumahray kaan aur tumhari ankhen aur chamray tumahray khilaaf shahadat den ge balkay tum yeh khayaal karte they ke khuda ko tumahray bohat se amlon ki khabar hi nahi
  41,23,aur isi khayaal ne jo tum apne perwar-digaar ke baray mein rakhtay they tum ko halaak kardiya aur tum khasara panay walon mein hogaye
  41,24,ab agar yeh sabr karen ge to un ka thikana dozakh hai. aur agar tauba karen ge to un ki tauba qubool nahi ki jaye gi
  41,25,aur hum ne ( shaitano ko ) un ka hum nasheen muqarrar kardiya tha to unhon ne un ke aglay aur pichlle aamaal un ko umdah kar dukhaay they aur jaanat aur insanon ki jamaten jo un se pehlay guzar chakain un par bhi khuda ( ke azaab ) ka wada poora hogaya. be shak yeh nuqsaan uthany walay hain
  41,26,aur kafir kehnay lagey ke is quran ko suna hi nah karo aur ( jab parhnay lagen to ) shore macha diya karo taakay tum ghalib raho
  41,27,so hum bhi kafiroon ko sakht azaab ke mazay chkhayin ge aur un ke buray amlon ki jo woh karte they saza den ge
  41,28,yeh khuda ke dushmanon ka badla hai ( yani ) dozakh. un ke liye isi mein hamesha ka ghar hai. yeh is ki saza hai ke hamari aayton se inkaar karte they
  41,29,aur kafir kahin ge ke ae hamaray perwar-digaar junoo aur insanon mein se jin logon ne hum ko gumraahkiya tha un ko hamein dikha ke hum un ko apne paon ke taley ( roond ) dalain taakay woh nihayat zaleel hon
